    # --- CORRECTED & INTEGRATED ADAPTIVE LOGIC ---
    # This section now creates a proper OR condition. The AI will attack if:
    #   - trigger1 (Normal Footsie): The standard random chance is met.
    #   - OR trigger2 (High-Confidence): The AI brain detects a clear vulnerability.
    
